snippet.title: Bannerman - Trailer
snippet.description:
NOW AVAILABLE!
http://www.bannermangame.com

Buy Bannerman on steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/456170/Bannerman/

--

Bannerman is a dark medieval action/adventure with a focus on historically accurate combat and challenging skill-based swordfighting! Bannerman will be coming to PC on the 31st of August, 2017!

For more information on Bannerman, head on over to http://www.bannermangame.com or check out the series "Just Make Game", here on the Armitage Games YouTube Channel!
